[[Category:en/Manual/Settings & Preferences]]

Enables right click emulation on systems that do not have a right mouse button. To use this press ctrl and then click (or hold) the left mouse button to perform actions as if you are clicking the right mouse button. This is a client-setting only.


'''Valid options:''' [ true | false ]

'''Default:''' false


''MeusH's comment: Be aware this can make mess with shared orders and many other functions using ctrl+click''